2) Music variables:
    chords (interval value)
    scales (note value)
        natural, flat, sharp

    Map note: value


3) Sound files
    note sound
    sound dict


4) Sound playing:
    pygame.mixer channels
    play note


5) Test all sound files


6) display piano keys:
    drawing surface
    draw keys


7) Class Button:
    .draw()
