    .ispressed()


8) User input variable:
    input note
    input chord


9) Detect mouse input:
    get pressed key
    get mouse input
    store input note
    display input note


10) Sound playing:
    press space to play selected note


11) Display chord buttons:
    drawing surface
    draw buttons  (using grid for placement)


12) Detect mouse input:
    get pressed chord
    get mouse input
    store input chord
    display input chord


13) Highlight pressed keys
14) Highlight pressed chord

15) Sound playing:
    play chords


 Bonus features:
    display note on music staff



